{"tid":2422074,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"未上市的 RTX3060 顯卡在日本市場已被炒作至 80000 日圓","createTime":"2021-02-25T02:58:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T04:08:13.000Z","uid":15564,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b4530250eec496c00382e66eb0538a81c577b3f0","tid":2422074,"uid":15564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T02:58:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.xfastest.com/cryptocurrency/91500/rtx3060-in-jp-80000-jpy/?fbclid=IwAR0eAtwpTDFDNo1Tvn1pfKbh6iwaRRjvmVhi4FHjyOI2_y2T0H4HgNfxnlg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.xfastest.com%2Fcryptocurrency%2F91500%2Frtx3060-in-jp-80000-jpy%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0eAtwpTDFDNo1Tvn1pfKbh6iwaRRjvmVhi4FHjyOI2_y2T0H4HgNfxnlg&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFXwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=99d5bf1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.xfastest.com/cryptocurrency/91500/rtx3060-in-jp-80000-jpy/?fbclid=IwAR0eAtwpTDFDNo1Tvn1pfKbh6iwaRRjvmVhi4FHjyOI2_y2T0H4HgNfxnlg</a><br />\n<br />\n距離 NVIDIA RTX 3060 顯卡上市的時間已經不久了，當然畢竟近期礦工搶卡的情況還是相當嚴重，因此可以預見縱使是 NVIDIA 已經聲稱將 RTX 3060 的挖礦能力做出限制，但沒意外應該還是無法應付礦工的需求量，而且近期也有 偷跑的消息 指出，挖非 ETHash 算法的幣種，例如 RVN、Conflux、Grin、Beam、Aeternity 這些基本上都不會受到算力限制。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.xfastest.com/data/attachment/forum/202102/24/220114lvn5vnnhxpnypedh.jpg.thumb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xfastest.com%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F202102%2F24%2F220114lvn5vnnhxpnypedh.jpg.thumb.jpg&h=ad520f6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據推特的爆料人士 @momomo_us 的消息指出，在日本的一些商家中，RTX 3060 12G 分別出現了 78980 與 88750 日圓的價格，並且都已經被訂購完畢，約折合 20000 台幣的售價已經比當年 RTX 3070 的開賣售價還要更高了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.xfastest.com/data/attachment/forum/202102/24/215855idjdz6jrbddhjdqt.jpg.thumb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xfastest.com%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F202102%2F24%2F215855idjdz6jrbddhjdqt.jpg.thumb.jpg&h=b82ae30c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNicehash 目前也出現了預估的 RTX 3060 挖礦收益預估計算器，NVIDIA RTX 3060 一天的挖礦收益還是有著 3.93 美金，假設以每天 0.25 美金的電費來看，扣除後單卡每月還有約 110 美金的收益進帳，假設幣價不變，總使一張要價 20000 台幣的 RTX 3060，連續挖礦 6.5 個月即可回本買卡的錢。<br />\n<br />\n參考資料 : @momomo_us Twitter、Nicehash"},{"pid":"7c7a708d61f4678c4557159da08abbafee02a774","tid":2422074,"uid":393322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T03:00:53.000Z","msg":"唔係話eth 跌緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa1351f0a78455d8b5dfc7e2c3bb89c8be8f9a2c","tid":2422074,"uid":15564,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T03:01:11.000Z","msg":"RTX 3060 DX12遊戲性能曝光　快2070少少<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gameapps.hk/news/43623/RTX-3060\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gameapps.hk%2Fnews%2F43623%2FRTX-3060&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFXwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=57bfeba5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gameapps.hk/news/43623/RTX-3060</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.gameapps.hk/images/202102/23/c1b937a06c97dd6d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F202102%2F23%2Fc1b937a06c97dd6d.jpg&h=1738dc6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日前，在DX12遊戲《Ashes of the Singularity》中，i7-8700K裝置RTX 3060平台的基準測試成績曝光，1080P平均成績6800分，畫面69.8FPS。對比發現，RTX 3060大約比RTX 2060提升了19%，比RTX 2070提升了9%。"},{"pid":"82308be95c5e2c17f81dfab5accc2d899a571d6a","tid":2422074,"uid":15564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T03:01:53.000Z","msg":"老黃出張垃圾卡都炒到咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f856a1d70020e293c3c3dd0dad5558e9f24b678","tid":2422074,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T03:03:00.000Z","msg":"日本都咁多礦工？"},{"pid":"46a8b2d885ffa3ef08d3c4c6f935552324baa9a5","tid":2422074,"uid":15564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7c7a708d61f4678c4557159da08abbafee02a774","tid":2422074,"uid":393322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T03:00:53.000Z","msg":"唔係話eth 跌緊